snippet.title: Williams Arcade Classics gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Williams Arcade Classics, Dos PC game produced by Digital Eclipse Software in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/williams-arcade-classics/8369/
Williams Arcade Classics ESWT a nice game style arcade platformer. In this game you must give proof of dexterity and speed. Is a compilation that includes many games.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
